---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio - Manolia Kocaoglu">
	<!-- Grille de fond -->
	<div class="grid-bg"></div>
	
	<!-- Éléments décoratifs pixelisés -->
	<div class="pixel-decorations">
		<div class="pixel-shape" style="top: 10%; left: 5%;"></div>
		<div class="pixel-shape" style="top: 20%; left: 20%;"></div>
		<div class="pixel-shape" style="top: 30%; right: 5%;"></div>
		<div class="pixel-shape" style="bottom: 20%; right: 15%;"></div>
		<div class="pixel-cross" style="top: 15%; right: 20%;"></div>
		<div class="pixel-plus" style="bottom: 40%; left: 5%;"></div>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<nav class="top-nav">
			<a href="/" class="back-btn">← Accueil</a>
			<div class="logo">⌂</div>
			<div class="social-icons">
				<a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">in</a>
				<a href="#" aria-label="Behance">Be</a>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Grid 2x2 de projets -->
		<main class="projects-layout">
			<!-- Projet INKSPIRE (top left) -->
			<article class="project-card large">
				<h2>INKSPIRE</h2>
				<p class="card-subtitle">Plateforme de tatouage par IA</p>
				
				<div class="project-mockup">
					<!-- Placeholder pour mockup -->
					<div class="mockup-placeholder">
                        <img src="/src/images/inspire.webp" alt="INKSPIRE Mockup" />
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="project-text">
					<p><strong>Objectif :</strong> Aider à visualiser son futur tatouage.</p>
					<p><strong>Design :</strong> Identité sobre, inspirée des studios de tatouage.</p>
					<p><strong>Expérience :</strong> Simple, mobile-first, en 3 étapes.</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Harmonie Colorée (top right) -->
            <article class="project-card">
				<h2>Harmonie colorée</h2>
				
				<div class="color-circles">
					<div class="circle" style="background: #1a1a1a;"></div>
					<div class="circle" style="background: #5a5a5a;"></div>
					<div class="circle" style="background: #9a9a9a;"></div>
					<div class="circle" style="background: #f5f5f5;"></div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="project-text">
					<p>L'harmonie colorée d'Inkspire repose sur un contraste fort entre le noir et le blanc, directement inspiré de l'univers du tatouage.</p>
					<p>Ce choix volontairement minimaliste met en valeur les visuels sans détourner l'attention et renforce l'élégance et la sobriété de l'identité.</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Typographie (bottom left) -->
			<article class="project-card">
				<h2>Typographie</h2>
				
				<div class="typography-display">
					<div class="font-sample">
						<span class="font-name">Montserrat Alternates</span>
						<div class="font-weights">
							<span class="weight-bold">Bold</span>
							<span class="weight-medium">Medium</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="font-sample nosifer-font">
						<span class="font-name-large">NOSIFER</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="project-text">
					<p>Montserrat Alternates, en Bold et Medium, apporte modernité et clarté à l'interface. En contraste, Nosifer est utilisée avec parcimonie pour rappeler l'encre et l'univers du tatouage, ajoutant une touche artistique forte à l'ensemble.</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Crédits (bottom right) -->
			<article class="project-card credits">
				<h2>Crédits</h2>
				
				<div class="project-text">
					<p>Ce projet a été réalisé dans le cadre d'un travail collectif. Un grand merci à Eva Lacroix et Victor Landwerlin pour leur créativité, leur implication et l'énergie qu'ils ont apportées à Inkspire. Leur collaboration a été essentielle pour donner vie à ce projet.</p>
					<p>Si vous souhaitez explorer notre projet, vous pouvez y accéder ci-dessous.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="credits-footer">
					<div class="manolia-avatar">
						<img src="/manolia.svg" alt="Manolia" />
					</div>
					<button class="cta-button">
						<span>Voir le projet</span>
						<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
							<path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						</svg>
					</button>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	:global(body) {
		background: #1a237e;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.grid-bg {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background-image: 
			linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
		background-size: 50px 50px;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.pixel-decorations {
		position: fixed;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.pixel-shape,
	.pixel-cross,
	.pixel-plus {
		position: absolute;
		width: 20px;
		height: 20px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.pixel-cross {
		width: 16px;
		height: 16px;
		background: 
			linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 10px, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 10px),
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 10px, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 10px);
		animation-delay: 1s;
	}

	.pixel-plus {
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		clip-path: polygon(
			40% 0%, 60% 0%, 60% 40%, 100% 40%, 
			100% 60%, 60% 60%, 60% 100%, 40% 100%, 
			40% 60%, 0% 60%, 0% 40%, 40% 40%
		);
		animation-delay: 2s;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.6; }
		50% { transform: translateY(-15px); opacity: 1; }
	}

	.container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		height: 100vh;
		width: 100vw;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		padding: 20px;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	/* Navigation */
	.top-nav {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 20px 20px;
	}

	.back-btn {
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1rem;
		padding: 10px 20px;
		border: 2px solid white;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		background: transparent;
	}

	.back-btn:hover {
		background: white;
		color: #1a237e;
		transform: translateX(-5px);
	}

	.logo {
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: white;
	}

	.social-icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 15px;
	}

	.social-icons a {
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		padding: 8px 12px;
		border: 2px solid white;
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.social-icons a:hover {
		background: white;
		color: #1a237e;
	}

	/* Layout principal - grille 2x2 */
	.projects-layout {
		flex: 1;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
		grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 20px;
		min-height: 0;
	}

	.project-card {
		background: white;
		border: 5px solid white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 30px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.project-card:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}

	.project-card.large {
		grid-row: span 2;
	}

	/* Titres */
	.project-card h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
		color: #1a237e;
		margin: 0 0 8px 0;
		letter-spacing: 3px;
	}

	.card-subtitle {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0 0 20px 0;
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	}

	/* INKSPIRE mockup */
	.project-mockup {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin: 20px 0;
	}

	.mockup-placeholder {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: #f5f5f5;
		border: 2px dashed #ccc;
		border-radius: 8px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		color: #999;
	}

	/* Cercles de couleur */
	.color-circles {
		display: flex;
		gap: 15px;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 30px 0;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.circle {
		width: clamp(50px, 6vw, 80px);
		height: clamp(50px, 6vw, 80px);
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	/* Typographie */
	.typography-display {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		padding: 20px 0;
	}

	.font-sample {
		margin-bottom: 25px;
	}

	.font-name {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #333;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	}

	.font-weights {
		display: flex;
		gap: 20px;
		font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1.1rem);
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	}

	.weight-bold {
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.weight-medium {
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.nosifer-font {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.font-name-large {
		font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		color: #1a237e;
		display: block;
	}

	/* Textes de description */
	.project-text {
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 0.9vw, 0.85rem);
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: #333;
		margin-top: auto;
	}

	.project-text p {
		margin: 0 0 10px 0;
	}

	.project-text strong {
		color: #1a237e;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	/* Crédits footer */
	.credits-footer {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-top: 20px;
		padding-top: 20px;
		border-top: 2px solid #eee;
	}

	.manolia-avatar {
		width: clamp(50px, 6vw, 70px);
		height: clamp(50px, 6vw, 70px);
		border-radius: 50%;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: white;
		border: 3px solid #522546;
	}

	.manolia-avatar img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	/* Bouton CTA */
	.cta-button {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		padding: 12px 24px;
		background: white;
		color: #1a237e;
		border: 3px solid #1a237e;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
		font-size: clamp(0.5rem, 0.7vw, 0.65rem);
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		background: #1a237e;
		color: white;
		transform: translateX(5px);
	}

	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 1200px) {
		.projects-layout {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			grid-template-rows: auto;
		}

		.project-card.large {
			grid-row: span 1;
		}

		.container {
			overflow-y: auto;
		}

		:global(body) {
			overflow: auto;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.container {
			padding: 15px;
		}

		.top-nav {
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 10px;
		}

		.project-card {
			padding: 20px;
		}

		.social-icons {
			order: 3;
			width: 100%;
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}
</style>

<script>
	// Animation d'entrée des cards
	const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.project-card');
	cards.forEach((card, index) => {
		card.style.opacity = '0';
		card.style.transform = 'scale(0.95)';
		
		setTimeout(() => {
			card.style.transition = 'all 0.5s ease';
			card.style.opacity = '1';
			card.style.transform = 'scale(1)';
		}, 100 + (index * 100));
	});
</script>